CustomField.description: The unique name of a Force.com Flow which will be executed every time a kanban card enters the zone. This is NOT the "Flow Name", but rather the "Unique Name" which has no spaces.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Enter the unique name of a Force.com Flow which will be executed every time a kanban card enters the zone. This is NOT the "Flow Name", but rather the "Unique Name" which was given to the flow upon creation.
CustomField.label: Entry Flow Name
